 This is to let students know her to prepare for lectures beginning soon.<\/p>\n<p>See Also: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/stu-course-registration-portal\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">STU Course Registration Portal | St. Thomas University Fall 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-is-included-in-the-offer-letter-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_Included_in_the_Offer_Letter_2024\"><\/span>What is Included in the Offer Letter 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Important information about your Degree Program, Scholarship offer (if applicable), Financial Assistance, Residence, and more is included with your offer. Any conditions associated with your offer will appear in your offer letter.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/d162s0cet9s8p8.cloudfront.net\/collegelogos\/423_stu.png\" alt=\"St. Thomas University STU Offer Letter\" width=\"286\" height=\"213\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-accept-the-stu-offer-letter-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Accept_the_STU_Offer_Letter_2024\"><\/span>How to Accept the STU Offer Letter\u00a0 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To accept the admission offers and download acceptance letter, follow this instructions below, pay deposit fees as indicated.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Log on to the\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.stu.ca\/myaccount\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Application Portal<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Click Accept Admission Offer<\/li>\n<li>Download the Offer Letter.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>For more information, kindly send us a feedback message and we will attend to you in a moment.<\/p>\n<p>ALso Check: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/stu-fall-academic-calendar-2024\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">STU Winter Academic Calendar 2024 | St. Thomas University<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Was the information useful? Like and share this post.<\/p>\n","protecte